{"tid":222834,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖) 發夢是如果看到他，代表你。。。。。。","createTime":"2017-04-29T22:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T09:50:18.000Z","uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b2b4d5dc56919bb85854311f3128440c701d9db","tid":222834,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T22:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xpRQ9ob.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxpRQ9ob.jpg&h=dafee319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在2006年時美國紐約有一名病患曾向精神科醫生求助，表示不斷夢到這個素未謀面的男子，並且將其面貌畫下來，過沒多久 醫師發現，原來許多人都有夢過他，於是就發起尋人的活動，不過至今仍一無所獲，沒有證據可以顯示男子確實存在，而且，指認的4000多人都沒有共通點。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://polymerhk.com/articles/2016/08/28/34250/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpolymerhk.com%2Farticles%2F2016%2F08%2F28%2F34250%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=1ca67685\" target=\"_blank\">http://polymerhk.com/articles/2016/08/28/34250/</a>"},{"pid":"b92edc056325a074c4d1dacf56f274f727666827","tid":222834,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T22:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848c97a4be8e3f2bb3653323eab4065007412672","tid":222834,"uid":48165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T22:42:01.000Z","msg":"發咗新聞出嚟多人見過咪夢到囉，屌你老母見過一個樣潛意識就會記得發夢就發到㗎啦"},{"pid":"0f65b1d1503dec99a195175eae4b190a0bdba247","tid":222834,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T22:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發咗新聞出嚟多人見過咪夢到囉，屌你老母見過一個樣潛意識就會記得發夢就發到㗎啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f43998b3642121487e8882cf500074a383e65e","tid":222834,"uid":5944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T06:19:15.000Z","msg":"方中信？"},{"pid":"3ad721a6a488e833d48f44eb1c3b2f4494853fe4","tid":222834,"uid":66234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0